&lt;li&gt;Document tracker structure and definitions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propose a standard process for ongoing inventory updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recommend improvements for long-term scalability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
